<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Seat Booking - SURF Example</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #eee;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #00d4ff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .explanation {
            background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #a78bfa;
        }

        .explanation strong {
            color: #00d4ff;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .event-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .event-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .event-info h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .event-info p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        .availability {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .availability-label {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .availability-count {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .availability-count.high {
            color: #22c55e;
        }

        .availability-count.medium {
            color: #eab308;
        }

        .availability-count.low {
            color: #ef4444;
        }

        .update-indicator {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #666;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        /* Selector Card */
        .selector-card {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .selector-label {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .seat-counter {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .counter-btn {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
            background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            color: #00d4ff;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .counter-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
            background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: #00d4ff;
        }

        .counter-btn:disabled {
            opacity: 0.3;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        .counter-value {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            min-width: 80px;
        }

        .total-price {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #a78bfa;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .total-price span {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #00d4ff;
        }

        .book-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7c3aed, #00d4ff);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .book-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .book-btn:disabled {
            opacity: 0.5;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        .state-display {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .state-display .label {
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .state-display .local {
            color: #22c55e;
        }

        .state-display .server {
            color: #00d4ff;
        }

        .back {
            position: fixed;
            top: 1rem;
            left: 1rem;
            color: #888;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .back:hover {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .warning {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <a href="/examples/05-state-survival" class="back">‚Üê Back</a>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>üé´ Echo Rule: Mixed State</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Local selection survives server updates</p>

        <div class="explanation">
            <strong>üí° Key Concept:</strong> Your seat selection is <em>local Cell state</em>.
            Available seats come from the <em>server</em> and update automatically.
            <br><br>
            Watch how your selection persists even as the server updates availability!
        </div>

        <!-- Event Info Card -->
        <div class="card">
            <div class="event-header">
                <div class="event-icon">üé∏</div>
                <div class="event-info">
                    <h2>Rock Concert 2026</h2>
                    <p>March 15, 2026 ‚Ä¢ 20:00 ‚Ä¢ Arena Stadium</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Server-updated availability (auto-refreshes every 3 seconds) -->
            <div id="availability-surface" d-auto-refresh="3000" d-auto-refresh-url="/api/seats">
                <div class="availability">
                    <div>
                        <div class="availability-label">Available Seats</div>
                        <div class="availability-count high" id="seat-count">--</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: right;">
                        <div class="availability-label">Price per seat</div>
                        <div style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem;">$75</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="update-indicator">Loading...</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- User Selection Card (Cell state) -->
        <div class="card selector-card" d-cell="{count: 1}" d-id="booking">
            <div class="selector-label">How many seats?</div>

            <div class="seat-counter">
                <button class="counter-btn" d-signal="click: count = Math.max(count - 1, 1)">‚àí</button>
                <div class="counter-value" d-text="count">1</div>
                <button class="counter-btn" d-signal="click: count = Math.min(count + 1, 10)">+</button>
            </div>

            <div class="total-price">
                Total: <span>$</span><span d-text="count * 75">75</span>
            </div>

            <button class="book-btn" d-pulse="action" d-action="/api/book-seats">
                üéüÔ∏è Book Now
            </button>

            <!-- State Visualization (inside Cell ‚Äî powered by d-text, zero JS) -->
            <div class="state-display">
                <div class="label">Current State:</div>
                <div><span class="local">üì± Local (Cell):</span> count: <span d-text="count">1</span></div>
                <div><span class="server">üåê Server:</span> available: <span id="debug-available">--</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../../partials/core-scripts') %>
</body>

</html>